Origin Forme: Dialga is in its Origin Forme when exposed to an Adamant Crystal as an Ext ended Action. Exposing it in Origin Forme reverts it to its Altered Forme (found in the Main PokDex).
Palkia is in its Origin Forme when exposed to a Lustrous Globe as an Extended Action. Exposing it in Origin Forme reverts it to its Altered Forme (found in the Main PokDex).

Therian Forme: The User changes to its Therian Forme if holding a Reveal Glass and uses its Incarnate Form otherwise.
